      "content": "yeah. stillness. that sounds a lot better than this constant, exhausting movement to nowhere. it's like everyone else is obsessed with finding the next stop, but i'm just ready to close the guidebook and settle in. do you think there's any point in continuing the trek once you've already realized where it's all leading?",
